You have a glitch (mol is hardcoded) in the code of the first function. 
The times are similar, after correcting for that glitch.

Note:
- grep("[[:digit:]]", ...) behaves almost twice as slow as grep("[0-9]", 
...)!
- corrected results below;

Sincerely,

Leonard
